data.description: Come see this nice brick home on the outskirts of Lawton's eastside!  Brand new roof Aug 2023 and the inside of the home was painted Sep 2023!  Plenty of room for all in this 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathrooms, 2 living areas and 2 dining areas with a 2 car garage all on a half acre lot!  As you enter the home, there is a small formal living area and formal dining area that open up to the den with the cozy fireplace and the kitchen.  The kitchen has nice wood/stain cabinets, granite counters and stainless steel appliances.  The main bedroom is on one side of the home with nice LPV flooring and a huge ensuite featuring a separate large tiled shower, jacuzzi tub, makeup vanity, double sink vanity and a great walk-in closet. On the other side of the home is the other 3 bedrooms and a nice bathroom. There is a guest half bath as well!  Outside is mature landscaping, a privacy fence, a storage building and super nice pergola to enjoy the views.  MacArthur School District!  Move-in ready!
